This Rails 3.1.0.rc6 projet should help the Rubymine developers to fix guard support ASAP ;)


Check out RUBY-8514 "Support Signal Handling when running ruby scripts inside Rubymine to support Guard" ticket
for details and a screncast!

http://youtrack.jetbrains.net/issue/RUBY-8514

To lauch guard from Rubymine, run run_guard.rb